Quote:  Prior to the floods the indications were such that the directors and shareholders fully believed that the dredge was about to realise expectations. For the few hours that she was on the first bottom, coarse, rusty gold, characteristic of that particular place, was got, but the river rose again, and another opportunity did not occur.
